description: This file defines a MockData class that provides static mock data for menu items and categories in a restaurant frontend application. It contains a list of MenuItem objects representing various menu entries with attributes like id, name, description, category, price, image, and flags for featured or popular items.

classes.name: MockData
classes.description: A class providing static mock data for menu items and categories, used for testing or development purposes.

methods.name: menu
methods.description: Provides a static list of MenuItem objects representing different menu entries with their details.

methods.name: categories
methods.description: Provides a static list of category names for filtering menu items.
